  m_Name: D2FMD
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - "\u2026\u2026."
  - "Heard from the other guy earlier that you\u2019re in."
  - "Just so you know, I can\u2019t stand people like you, only thing you care about
    is your little \u201Cfamily\u201D  and all the adjacent bullshit."
  - "Everyone in this fucking town is obsessed with it, you wanna go out or do anything
    ? It\u2019s always meeting people, seeing friends, finding a partner."
  - Someone like me? Government gives nothing, no place, no purpose, no anything.
  - ":  But whatever, you\u2019re willing to cooperate so you\u2019re better than
    most at least"
  - 'You: Oh, thank you. I hope I can be of good help.'
  - Yeah, sure, great.
  - "Anyways, to get you up to speed, I imagine you\u2019ve heard those rumours going
    around, about the hiding of symptoms? "
  - "Yeah, we\u2019ve got no hard proof yet, but I\u2019ll tell you one thing, it\u2019s
    way worse than you think. "
  - "All these bullshit decisions and announcements that they\u2019re making are
    part of their greater plan, and it\u2019s not one that\u2019s benefitting anyone
    living in this dome. They\u2019re hiding much more about all this than just symptoms."
  - "That\u2019s all, expect messages later, we\u2019ll have things for you to do."
